    <item>
      <title>Aamu.app Docs - feature overview</title>
      <link>https://aamu.app/blog/posts/aamuapp-docs-feature-overview/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 22:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://aamu.app/blog/posts/aamuapp-docs-feature-overview/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34;&gt;Let’s see the Docs main page. It has all the familiar elements:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34; src=&#34;459044995593e728_image.png&#34; style=&#34;width: auto; --upload-progress: 0%;&#34; id=&#34;86c169de-1d5f-49ed-b34e-7e56df58aa01&#34;&gt;&lt;ol xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Project picker (or all projects)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add new Doc&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Doc box&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Search&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34;&gt;Let’s create a new doc:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34; src=&#34;feee620816b63169_image.png&#34; style=&#34;width: auto; --upload-progress: 0%;&#34; id=&#34;da6d07c7-23eb-4f23-9a50-b3bff1b90bd9&#34;&gt;&lt;p xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34;&gt;We are met with a title and the content area. What else do we need at this stage? Let’s add a title:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34; src=&#34;1935c020868f20ea_image.png&#34; style=&#34;width: auto; --upload-progress: 0%;&#34; id=&#34;3abb81fc-ce18-44be-8788-4fa49ae542cf&#34;&gt;&lt;p xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&#34;&gt;So, we got a bit more. A project picker, File menu, &lt;em&gt;Publish&lt;/em&gt; button, Chat section, tags, current editors.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
